---
title: Dukkah-Crusted Chicken & Yoghurt with Veggie-Loaded Currant Couscous
description: You can truly throw just about anything into a couscous and watch the magic happen, but we’re putting on a real show tonight with a slice of chicken, crusted in dukkah. Make sure not to miss our hidden trick with the currants (psst, they’re tossed in the couscous), they’re the closing act to go alongside the chicken.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/648baa0f783f8229494a7ffe-53de34e7.png
